snippet.title: Amber Heard - Her plan worked? Johnny Depp's failure boosts her career?
snippet.description:
If you thought that now that the court case is over you won't be hearing about Amber Heard and Johnny Depp then I must sadly disappoint you. With the recent verdict announced by the judge, and Depp's loss and leaving his role as Grindelwald in the Fantastic Beast's franchise, many are now calling for Warner Bros to remove Heard from her role in Aquaman. But will their protests have any effect? #AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #Aquaman
